                <span id="Label1"><div>Revised and Updated<br><br>Indispensable as ever, Oz Clarke's now-classic pocket wine guide has been revised and updated for 2004, including much anticipated lists of "World Class Wines That Don't Cost the Earth," "Best Lookalikes to the Classics," and "The 10 Best-Kept Secrets." <br>As accessible as it is complete, Oz Clarke's Pocket Wine Guide 2004 lists each wine, grape, winery, producer, and region alphabetically. It is a perfect pocket reference for novices-and essential for the seasoned wine lover wanting the latest information.<br></div></span>
              
